{"tid":813750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲女童蔡穎妍 失蹤近1個月","createTime":"2018-09-10T16:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T23:23:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"33ba218624fd8bc08ac79576313a4f8d0328b1fe","tid":813750,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180910/large/1536564153_9bad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180910%2Flarge%2F1536564153_9bad.jpg&h=2fead989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方今日呼籲市民提供一名在葵涌失蹤女童的消息。14歲女童蔡穎妍於8月7日晚上離開其位於石籬（二）邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於8月12日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n蔡穎妍身高約1.65米，瘦身材，尖面型，黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿黑白色間條短袖上衣、黑色牛仔短褲及白色運動鞋。<br />\n<br />\n任何人士如有蔡穎妍的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 1176或5613 6963或電郵至rmpu-nts-2@police.gov.hk與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"8a4c9224f4a91752f8e65420649f6d03a52955d5","tid":813750,"uid":6959,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf749f54ff2fcde13fd263d048ce33d41b2165c8","tid":813750,"uid":7699,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"張相似34喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e704d473b8cae4cc657fef4d4a335d1bdf77e519","tid":813750,"uid":35451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"個樣完全唔似14<br />\n仲要米65"},{"pid":"16f1d48c1d8cbfb9b825582b6d8176aadebe8b47","tid":813750,"uid":5715,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會係男朋友屋企啊"},{"pid":"4ef3bd922b88d824ca52b61906498ee4293d362e","tid":813750,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201809/10/P2018091000609_photo_1142949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.